quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,119,"Mana toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubalia bakholanga obubii khubulamanya mana nibekanila nibakhakhola ako, mana nibakhola amalayi, toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olunyuma lwa ako ni Omunji wokhuleshela, Omunji westimbabaasi."
  16,120,"Toto Ibrahim yali Omwimilisi, Omwihotselefu khu Nyasaye, Omutswenufu, ne shiyali mubatsokaasi tawe."
  16,121,"Yali omukhupi wa orio khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye. Mana namwawula ne namulunjisia khunjila ingololofu."
  16,122,"Mana nikhumuhelesia mushialo amalayi, naye toto mwikulu aliba mubandu abalayi."
  16,123,"Mana nikhukhufimbulila mbu: “Loonda emilukha chia Ibrahim omulunjifu, ne shiyali mubatsokaasi tawe.”"
  16,124,"Toto Jumamosi yarebwaho khubalia bakabukhanamwo khuyo, ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, alikhalaka eshina hakari wabu inyanga yeyindukho khukalia akabakabukhanangamwo."
  16,125,"Langa khunjila ya Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mumachesi, nende amachelo amalayi, ne olomalome nabo munjila indayi muno. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi amanyile muno ulia wakora ehale nende injila yiyie, ne amanyile muno balia abalunjikha."
  16,126,"Ne nimurunga imoongo, runge ebihelana nende ebia mukholelwe amabii. Ne nimwifwila, toto awo nobulayi khubalia abefwilanga."
  16,127,"Ne wifwile. Okhwifwila khukhwo khulaba halali khulwa Nyasaye butswa. Ne olabeelela shichila bo tawe. Ne olaba mubunyakhani shichila kabatutanga tawe."
  16,128,"Toto Nyasaye ali halala nende balia bamuria, nende balia abakholanga amalayi."